            Learn more about our Pharmacology catalog!
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" href=@Url.Action("PharmacologyCatalog")>Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Protocol Notebook</h2>
